data.description: Back on the market...Buyer decided they lost trust in their lender and backed out.  Main Level living Rancher is desirable location.  2 bedroom 1 Full Bath all brick Rancher on approx. 0.75 acres.  Home feature hardwood floors, open kitchen with island, breakfast nook, laundry room on main level, great yard, large deck and patio for a firepit.  If you like to spend time outdoors this is the home for you.  Home is back Witmer Lane off the beaten path but close to Alt 40, convenient to US 15, US340 and I70 for easy commuter location.  Check it out, wont last long.
